<h3 style="color: #3594dc; font-weight: normal;">Be sure to take a look at our Commercial Extensions, we have just released <a href="http://velite.de/extension/superflow"><strong style="text-decoration: underline;">Superflow for Magento</strong></a>, a brand new extension with many features that are highly customizable! Be sure to take a look at the interactive demo.</h3>
<p>You want to feature some special products? Then Magento Teaserbox should be the right tool for your needs. Simply attach your own teaser images to any product within your database and display them in the Teaserbox. Have a look at the <a href="http://velite.de/extension/teaserbox/demo">Demo</a> to see Teaserbox in action and play arround with the settings. For installation instructions take a look at the <a href="http://velite.de/extension/teaserbox/docs">Teaserbox Documentation</a>.</p>
<h4>Releaselog</h4>
<p>You can find information about what changed in the different Teaserbox versions in the Releaselog Thread: http://www.magentocommerce.com/boards/viewthread/52461/</p>
<h4>IMPORTANT: Magento 1.4</h4>
<p>If you're planing to install Teaserbox on a Magento 1.4 Shop please use the latest Teaserbox version (1.2.0 and above). The older Teaserbox versions cause problems together with Magento 1.4.</p>
<h4>Uninstallation</h4>
<p>Please notice that you will have to run an SQL Statement to uninstall the extension. http://www.magentocommerce.com/boards/viewthread/52022/.</p>";s:1:"r";a:1:{s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:10:"xlink:href";s:36:"/Chiara_PEAR_Server_REST/r/Teaserbox";}}}